                  <collation>
                    <p>The quires were originally 15 in number.</p>
                    <p>The quires are signed with Syriac letters, and also with either Greek letters or Syriac arithmetical figures; e.g. fol. <locus>20b</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܓ</foreign>; 
                      fol. <locus>41b</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܙ</foreign>; 
                      fol. <locus>44a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝ</foreign>; 
                      fol. <locus>57a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܓ</foreign>;
                      fol. <locus>67a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܕ</foreign>;
                      fol. <locus>77a</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܗ</foreign>.</p>
                    <!-- Enter arithmetical figures -->
                  </collation>
                  <condition>
                    <list>
                      <item>
                        <p>Some leaves are much stained and torn, especially foll. <locus>6</locus>, <locus>8</locus>, <locus>9</locus>, <locus>22</locus>, <locus>32</locus>, <locus>40</locus>, <locus>41</locus>, <locus>43</locus>, and <locus>48</locus>.</p>
                        <p>Leaves are wanting after foll. <locus>8</locus>, <locus>9</locus>, <locus>10</locus>, <locus>21</locus>, <locus>31</locus>, <locus>42</locus>, <locus>43</locus>, <locus>44</locus>, <locus>45</locus>, <locus>46</locus>, <locus>47</locus>, and <locus>56</locus>.</p>
                        <p>Quires <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܛ</foreign>, and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܐ</foreign> are lost, and several others are very imperfect.</p>
                   <!-- Enter arithmetical figures -->
                      </item>
